{"tid":1372313,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣令香討嘅人變成我哋嘅人","createTime":"2019-07-27T11:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T15:47:43.000Z","uid":284745,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa0216db0b75f0f78abba4c4562c4787366a188","tid":1372313,"uid":284745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:50:35.000Z","msg":"估唔到過多年，我仲有朋友用香討<br />\n而佢哋又好信裡面嘅人所講嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰度實在太多港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，個個圍爐取暖<br />\n睇唔到真相，好需要多啲聲音，鬧臭官商鄉黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我本身仲諗住喺香討留言<br />\n按咗回覆，竟然出咗呢個畫面：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ja8PThr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fja8PThr.png&h=7606e412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其他台嘅post又任留言<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vuogyhr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvuogyhr.png&h=bdeee063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得可以點樣大規模洗香討版呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69ea8549e84c84d0b52530ddcecac5552eb4f12","tid":1372313,"uid":48362,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:54:20.000Z","msg":"唔洗理佢地<br />\n由得佢地死<br />\n最好全部人都比黑警/武警/解放軍先姦後殺 不論男女老幼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5151b6a60fe13c32ef8286a1d88f8aef5261b03","tid":1372313,"uid":23951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:57:18.000Z","msg":"其實係有清醒嘅人，不過好多三毛推走/搞亂d正常嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312cd98520bcbde98feec2d3285e07efac11f8d6","